verses.text: Come let us praise \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* \w with|strong="H3068"\w* joy: let us joyfully sing \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H0410"\w* \w our|strong="H3068"\w* saviour.

\w For|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* sea \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w his|strong="H3068"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* made \w it|strong="H3068"\w*: \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w his|strong="H3068"\w* hands formed \w the|strong="H3068"\w* dry \w land|strong="H5159"\w*.

\w For|strong="H0430"\w* \w he|strong="H0430"\w* \w is|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H0559"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3050"\w* \w our|strong="H7200"\w* \w God|strong="H0430"\w*: \w and|strong="H0430"\w* \w we|strong="H7200"\w* \w are|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H0559"\w* \w people|strong="H3808"\w* \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w his|strong="H7200"\w* pasture \w and|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H0559"\w* sheep \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w his|strong="H7200"\w* hand.
Today if \w you|strong="H5971"\w* shall hear \w his|strong="H0995"\w* voice, harden not \w your|strong="H0995"\w* hearts:

\w As|strong="H8085"\w* \w in|strong="H8085"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* provocation, according \w to|strong="H8085"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* day \w of|strong="H5869"\w* temptation \w in|strong="H8085"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* wilderness: \w where|strong="H3808"\w* \w your|strong="H8085"\w* fathers tempted \w me|strong="H3808"\w*, \w they|strong="H0518"\w* proved \w me|strong="H3808"\w*, \w and|strong="H5869"\w* saw \w my|strong="H8085"\w* works.

Forty years long \w was|strong="H0120"\w* \w I|strong="H3808"\w* offended \w with|strong="H3198"\w* \w that|strong="H3808"\w* generation, \w and|strong="H0120"\w* \w I|strong="H3808"\w* said: These always err \w in|strong="H3808"\w* heart.

\w And|strong="H3068"\w* \w these|strong="H1992"\w* \w men|strong="H0120"\w* \w have|strong="H3045"\w* \w not|strong="H3588"\w* \w known|strong="H3045"\w* \w my|strong="H3068"\w* \w ways|strong="H4284"\w*: \w so|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* swore \w in|strong="H3068"\w* \w my|strong="H3068"\w* wrath \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w they|strong="H1992"\w* \w shall|strong="H3068"\w* \w not|strong="H3588"\w* enter into \w my|strong="H3068"\w* rest.
